  <brief_title>Study of Methylnaltrexone (MNTX) for the Relief of Constipation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Phase 3, Two-Week, Placebo Controlled Study of Methylnaltrexone(MNTX) for the Relief of Constipation Due to Opioid Therapy in Advance Medical Illness.</official_title>
